---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section id="contact" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl rounded-[32px] border border-[#d8e7d7] bg-white px-6 py-12 text-[#2b3f2c] shadow-sm">
	<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
		<div>
			<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#6f8770]">Contact</p>
			<h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black">X / GitHub から気軽にご連絡ください</h2>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#4a5f4c]">S3 でホストする静的サイトのため、連絡手段はシンプルに外部リンクへ誘導します。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex gap-4">
			<a
				class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d5e5d3] bg-[#f8fbf7] text-2xl transition hover:-translate-y-0.5"
				href="https://x.com/"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noreferrer"
				aria-label="Visit X profile"
			>
				✕
			</a>
			<a
				class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#d5e5d3] bg-[#f8fbf7] text-2xl transition hover:-translate-y-0.5"
				href="https://github.com/"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noreferrer"
				aria-label="Visit GitHub profile"
			>
				⚫
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-[#748473]">© {year} Takahiro&apos;s Portfolio</p>
</section>
